OL,4,CGive UK workers four more bank holidays
OL,5,Ca year, says TUC
OL,6, Workers in England and Wales are being
OL,7, fobbed off with a "stingy" number of
OL,8, bank holidays, say trades unions.
OL,10,FThey get eight public holidays a year,
OL,11,Fwhich is four fewer than the EU average
OL,12,Fand half the number in Japan.
OL,14,FThe umbrella body for unions, the TUC,
OL,15,Fis calling for a new public holiday
OL,16,Fbetween September and Christmas.
OL,18,FIt would be "a great way to thank
OL,19,Fworking Britain for getting us through
OL,20,Fthese tough times," TUC general
OL,21,Fsecretary Frances O'Grady said.
